'''亞當·斯科特'''（{{lang-en|Adam Derek Scott}}；{{bd|1980年|7月16日}}）是[[澳洲|澳洲]]的一位[[職業高爾夫球手|職業高爾夫球手]]，主要參加[[PGA巡迴賽|PGA巡迴賽]]。他在2014年5月中旬至8月是[[世界排名第一男子高爾夫球手列表|世界排名第一的高爾夫球手]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theage.com.au/sport/golf/adam-scott-no1-but-eyeing-a-bigger-prize-20140519-zrh3q.html |title=Adam Scott No.1 but eyeing a bigger prize |last1=Everill |first1=Ben |date=2014-05-19 |website=The Age |publisher=Fairfax Media |access-date=19 May 2014 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726162141/https://www.theage.com.au/sport/golf/adam-scott-no1-but-eyeing-a-bigger-prize-20140519-zrh3q.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他迄今已贏得31項職業賽事冠軍。

斯科特迄今贏得的最大賽事冠軍是{{link-en|2013年美國名人賽|2013 Masters Tournament}}，這是他的第一個[[四大賽|大滿貫]]冠軍，也令他成為迄今唯一贏得美國名人賽冠軍的澳洲球手<ref name="ESPN Adam Scott 1st Aussie">{{cite news |title=Adam Scott 1st Aussie to win Masters |url=http://espn.go.com/golf/masters13/story/_/id/9171606/2013-masters-adam-scott-beats-angel-cabrera-wins-green-jacket |access-date=2013-04-14 |work=ESPN |date=2013-04-14 |archive-date=2014-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325030507/http://espn.go.com/golf/masters13/story/_/id/9171606/2013-masters-adam-scott-beats-angel-cabrera-wins-green-jacket |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他還贏得過{{link-en|2004年球員錦標賽|2004 Players Championship}}、{{link-en|2011年普利司通邀請賽|2011 WGC-Bridgestone Invitational}}、{{link-en|2016年普利司通邀請賽|2016 WGC-Cadillac Championship}}等重要賽事的冠軍。在{{link-en|2012年英國高爾夫公開賽|2012 Open Championship}}上，他在最後四洞之前領先四桿，但最後因連續博忌而不敵[[厄尼·艾爾斯|厄尼·艾爾斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pga.com/openchampionship/news/adam-scotts-major-moment-ruined-late-struggles |title=Adam Scott blows Open Championship opportunity |date=2012-07-22 |publisher=PGA of America |first=Jim |last=Litke |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305231258/http://www.pga.com/openchampionship/news/adam-scotts-major-moment-ruined-late-struggles |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==個人生活==
斯科特出生在[[南澳州|南澳州]][[阿得雷德|阿得雷德]]，並在9歲時和家人一起搬到[[陽光海岸_(澳大利亞)|陽光海岸]]。1993年，他又和家人一起搬至[[黃金海岸_(澳大利亞)|黃金海岸]]。他在{{link-en|庫拉爾賓國際學校|Kooralbyn International School}}就讀高中課程，並在這一時期選擇了高爾夫球課程。他就讀於[[內華達大學拉斯維加斯分校|內華達大學拉斯維加斯分校]]，並加入過{{link-en|Sigma Chi兄弟會|Sigma Chi}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.presidentscup.com/news/2015/7/20/things-you-didn-t-know-about-adam-scott.html |title=Things you didn't know about Adam Scott |date=2015-07-28 |publisher=The Presidents Cup |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401160831/https://www.presidentscup.com/news/2015/7/20/things-you-didn-t-know-about-adam-scott.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年4月，斯科特和瑞典建築家瑪瑞爾·科雅（Marie Kojzar）在[[巴哈馬|巴哈馬]]舉辦了一場小型婚禮。兩人在2000年代初期至中期就曾長期交往過。雖然之後分手，但在2013年復活<ref name=Married>{{cite web |url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/adam-scott-weds-girlfriend-marie-kojzar-in-secret-ceremony-at-home/story-fnibbwxt-1226912566488 |title=Adam Scott weds girlfriend Marie Kojzar in secret ceremony at home |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2014-05-10 |website=Herald Sun |publisher=News Ltd |access-date=2014-05-10 |archive-date=2020-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404191253/http://www.heraldsun.com.au/sport/adam-scott-weds-girlfriend-marie-kojzar-in-secret-ceremony-at-home/story-fnibbwxt-1226912566488 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年2月，斯科特和科雅有了他們的第一個女兒Bo Vera Scott<ref>{{cite web |url=https://golfweek.usatoday.com/2015/02/16/adam-scott-pga-tour-baby-girl-birth-announcement/ |title=Adam Scott, wife welcome baby girl |date=2015-02-16 |publisher=Golfweek |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401160800/https://golfweek.usatoday.com/2015/02/16/adam-scott-pga-tour-baby-girl-birth-announcement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年8月18日，他們宣布了長子Byron Scott出生的消息<ref>{{cite web |url=https://golf.com/news/adam-scott-named-his-newborn-son-in-part-after-a-golf-legend/ |title=Adam Scott named his newborn son (in part) after a golf legend |date=2017-08-31 |publisher=Golf.com |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401160822/https://golf.com/news/adam-scott-named-his-newborn-son-in-part-after-a-golf-legend/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

斯科特曾經和女子網球前世界第一[[安娜·伊萬諾維奇|安娜·伊萬諾維奇]]在2010年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.golfgrinder.com/news/players/adam-scott-my-life-without-ana/ |title=Adam Scott: My life without Ana |date=2010-12-12 |publisher=Golf Grinder |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028081703/http://www.golfgrinder.com/news/players/adam-scott-my-life-without-ana/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和2011年交往過<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/star-sporting-duo-adam-scott-and-ana-ivanovic-split-ahead-of-aussie-tour/story-fn907478-1226551761839 |title=Star sporting duo Adam Scott and Ana Ivanovic split ahead of Aussie tour |newspaper=The Telegraph |date=2013-01-11 |access-date=2013-10-17 |archive-date=2013-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110103727/http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/celebrity/star-sporting-duo-adam-scott-and-ana-ivanovic-split-ahead-of-aussie-tour/story-fn907478-1226551761839 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

斯科特是一位狂熱的[[衝浪|衝浪]]愛好者<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theinertia.com/surf/adam-scott-linking-surfing-and-golf-highest-level-masters-champion/ |title=Adam Scott: Linking Surfing and Golf at the Highest Level |date=2013-04-18 |publisher=The inertia |access-date=2021-04-01 |archive-date=2020-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818081531/https://www.theinertia.com/surf/adam-scott-linking-surfing-and-golf-highest-level-masters-champion/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他是[[澳大利亞澳式足球聯盟|澳大利亞澳式足球聯盟]]球隊[[阿德萊德澳式足球會|阿德萊德烏鴉]]的球迷<ref>{{cite web|last1=Beveridge|first1=Riley|title=Your AFL club’s most famous supporters, from Barack Obama to Cam Newton|url=http://www.foxsports.com.au/afl/your-afl-clubs-most-famous-supporters-from-barack-obama-to-cam-newton/news-story/03eb54659866d587cf9c2cc4b9f3d8c5|website=Fox Sports|access-date=2016-01-29|archive-date=2017-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607232136/http://www.foxsports.com.au/afl/your-afl-clubs-most-famous-supporters-from-barack-obama-to-cam-newton/news-story/03eb54659866d587cf9c2cc4b9f3d8c5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。出於避稅目的，斯科特是[[瑞士|瑞士]]居民<ref name=BRW>{{cite web |url=http://brw.com.au/p/brw-lounge/setting_record_sportsman_golfer_Se6Y21tJ5o4Ow9OuZrj7qN |title=Our next $100m sportsman: Golfer Adam Scott eyes bigger prize after setting new record at Australian Open |last1=Heathcote |first1=Andrew |date=2013-11-29 |website=BRW Magazine |publisher=Fairfax Media |access-date=2013-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201185601/http://www.brw.com.au/p/brw-lounge/setting_record_sportsman_golfer_Se6Y21tJ5o4Ow9OuZrj7qN |archive-date=2013-12-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

